Map created by: Gangstakill
Decals created by: Enza

Map objective: Touch the wall at the opponent's spawn point. The wall is marked with the word "kill" in your team's corresponding color.

Spawnpoints: 24 (12V12)

This map is NOT made for deathmatch, Unless the server has a respawntimer of at least 5 seconds.
